          "from_upn": null,
          "sent_utc": "2026-06-29T11:25:08.157Z",
          "sent_mt": "2026-06-29T05:25:08-06:00",
          "text": "Rich Brierley, Shawn Jewkes\n\nA lot of the values are blank that help guide the team. \n\nCan we get these updated today?",
          "importance": "normal",
          "web_url": null
        },
        {
          "id": "1782734880702",
