          "from_upn": null,
          "sent_utc": "2026-06-29T12:08:00.702Z",
          "sent_mt": "2026-06-29T06:08:00-06:00",
          "text": "It's not missing, it got shredded into two pieces. It's in the office upstairs",
          "importance": "normal",
          "web_url": null
        },
        {
          "id": "1782734908902",
          "from": "Preston Elmer",
          "from_upn": null,
          "sent_utc": "2026-06-29T12:08:28.902Z",
          "sent_mt": "2026-06-29T06:08:28-06:00",
          "text": "We don't have any spares. But conveyors and equipment is going to come out as soon as they can today and bring us one they're going to make",
